Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:02.52,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)}時雨初空字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.02,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)}翻译：goldfish、 Crowst； 校对：無月；歌词：戦闘幽霊；\N定时：凑 智花； 繁化：戦闘幽霊； LOGO&特效：面麻； 后期：せんとう；
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,790)\c&H6D4B09&}想和大家 一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,木村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚—— 恭喜你们啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,教现代国语的木村和现代法学的守屋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有勇气…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里为止有什么不明白的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您和木村老师是什么时候开始交往的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,雄蕊给雌蕊授粉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,送子鸟已经来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.80,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40\3c&H000000&}注：送子鸟是指欧洲白鹤，在欧洲，有传言送子鸟在谁家屋顶造巢，谁家就会喜得贵子。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在卷心菜田里有没有收获什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.10,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40\3c&H000000&}注：这里也是在西方流传的说法，当孩子问起自己是从哪里来的，\N家长会告诉他「 你是从卷心菜田里捡来的」之类。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,准备什么时候生小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 肯定就是这么个展开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,直就是无法地带了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么木村老师 你和守屋老师开始交往的契机是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是同乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是聊天的时候慢慢地感觉很投缘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是同乡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:19.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 守屋老师~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,中午饭一起吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好恩❤爱啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恩爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,变得开始憧憬成为新娘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:43.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是当新娘来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那都什么时候的事了 嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还在学乘法的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有个看起来有点像新娘子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你你你…你在说谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 她好像不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为年幼所以认知力还很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没什么生前的记忆是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话可能会很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:54.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵是因为对什么东西心存留念 才能存在于这个世间的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:59.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个少女甚至连那份记忆也正在失去是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能无法实现她的执念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,最终就这样渐渐消矢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:11.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 创造一个就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,名为回忆的新的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…刚才说了很不错的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我来教你说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:29.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊 能说话不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说不定还会用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:39.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,「哥哥」来叫我昵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是笨蛋山田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,天海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,小川！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋山田！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,记得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这家伙是灼发的弥赛亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类能揍真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,上原同学！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是井上成美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,成美！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要教他至少拿本书啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,背过脸去害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像混得很熟的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是也×8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在偷偷教她些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你个自私的月代头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.32,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40\3c&H000000&}注：月代头就是古代日本武士所梳的发型。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是少数派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:28.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是也~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就记住怎样打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说得非常棒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:51.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,井上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,干 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没在看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:02.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再…再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是要分别时说的话哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:11.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的份也买了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候就应该说「谢谢」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:36.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「对不住」而是「抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向教育？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,（讨厌 真是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,（什么嘛…）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来接龙比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,从「mo」开始的词是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,moya\N守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,yamori\N壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,risu\N松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,sumomo\N李子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,moya~\N守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙太宠她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起很开心啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,身高…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 因为是大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说话已经很流畅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟以前一样什么都没想起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在说什么已经成谜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想不起来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有像我们这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,交心的朋友在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了很不错的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个先不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是老师他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守…屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋 守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 这个孩子和守屋老师是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是守屋被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是守屋的私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,其…其实是守屋老师的守护灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有回想起其他事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆直接让她见见守屋怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下难以苟同是也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还不知道那个少女是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也说不好会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,万一是对守屋殿下有害的事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这个的哪里会有害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说万一啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋老师和木村老师已经准备结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 还是稳妥一些的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样 那就由我去调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋老师和这个孩子的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没问出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别想笑着蒙混过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我稍微摆出点抱歉的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没问出来…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我们去调查啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,才 才不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了守屋老师他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,傲娇傲娇~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别教人家奇怪的话啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,天海你就陪着这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 很忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,天海同学 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来有点困扰的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你又搞什么幺蛾子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,被老师发现就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么麻烦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:10.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭马上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的是幽灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 让您陪着我们真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 反正也不怎么恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:44.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 总觉得很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了！多吃点哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,小女孩的幽灵在找守屋老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直「守屋 守屋」地这样喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道是个怎样的孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:05.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 头发长长的 穿着白色的连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那不是连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在医院住院的时候穿的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:15.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 守屋老师他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候身体不好 好像经常要去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有时也会长时间地住院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候有个和他住同一间病房的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为年龄也很相近 两个人很快就熟悉了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后好像就在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个孩子患的病比他严重得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,粗茶淡饭 不成敬意~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋老师 今天真的很谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 不可思议的事件也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一起玩什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 明天不能陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要举行结婚仪式了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋 要结婚…了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 因为守屋 也变大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是「大人」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,胡萝卜 也已经能吃下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:45.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 那个孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:07.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋老师小时候在医院认识的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是小时候的样子也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,今 今天不玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了要陪她玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,井上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~哦~强撑着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不坦诚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 来做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！那就来踢罐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就是鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我捡去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始了么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:50.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,汪汪~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 天海？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来跟我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:01.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,小川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:03.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,上原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,弥赛亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我弥赛亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 笨蛋山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我笨蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,（看我的）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,（住手！！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天玩得很过瘾昵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,开心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:53.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…一直在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这睡相…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,重新睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,天海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起玩了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,守屋~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果长大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果成为大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,变得帅帅的了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要再一次相见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没能遵守约定 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢守屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜~拜~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,绕许多的远路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,带着很多礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到 与那孩子相见的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要打工 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:29.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,打工什么的翘掉好了 然后大家一起去玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,懂不懂察言观色啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好的 大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哀悼一个人的感觉真的很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们去玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就山田请客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,等…为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,语言是知道了意思之后才会用的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,「再见」什么的 没听到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 那个孩子还是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,「陪我玩了很久 谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:31.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊 再多玩会儿不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,井上同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂~天海同学你们也快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也好后天也好 我们大家一直一起玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 预告什么的真心神烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事又不是小辣妹的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:50.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但情人节不管什么时代都一样啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:55.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！感觉刚才自己的语气超像大妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:24:00.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 响妹子也准备了情人节巧克力 是要给谁的呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:04.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 RE-KAN！「这是秘密的 情人节」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是「在情人节要三倍奉还」的感觉？
